Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.74,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}RELYING ON UNSEEN FORCES...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.28,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}KOKORO NO TOBIRA TOZASAZU NI TSUYOKU... TSUYOKU...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:18.28,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}POWERFULLY WITHOUT LOCKING UP THE HEART'S DOOR... POWERFULLY...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A courageous heart and deduction power!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm that leads us to the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange detached room in the legendary pond
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the water changes, the waterwheel turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a child with the mind of an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.30,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}WATASHI GA KANJITEITA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.30,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}MAYBE I WAS GIVING YOU PAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:47.06,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}TOGE OKIMI NI NO ONAJI\NYOU NI ATAETEITA NO KANO SHIRENAKATTA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:47.06,Dialogue,OP EN,0,0,0,,{\fs21}SIMILAR TO WHAT I'VE FELT, AND WITHOUT THINKING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:57.99,Dialogue Top,OP JP,0,0,0,,{\fs21}NANI NI KOKORO WO ITAMETE NANI NI OBIETEITA NO KA\NKI NI INO TOMEZU MOTSURETEKU FUTARI NO SHINJITSU NI
