Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-sama, as in the famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirou Suzuki from the Suzuki Financial Company
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,said that someone would come in place of him
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but to think it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please go easy on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, a tea ceremony's headmaster's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tea ceremonies... so formal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I should get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:29.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,The Water Palace of Five Colors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:29.75,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enchanting! What a fascinating view!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it shines in a yellow color?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time looking at a pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this time of year,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the water shines in five colors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,depending on which lay the sun is facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why this place is called the Water Palace of Five Colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:02:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,These are my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.29,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Antique Dealer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.29,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Morio Yakura (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The antique dealer, Yakura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yukari Mimura (33)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.71,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And a manager of a company, Mimura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the famous detective, Kogoro Mouri, and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:26.81,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Housekeeper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:26.81,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Yoshiko Hanasaki (40)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, now that we're all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll call Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The headmaster of the tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the hard-to-please headmaster\Nwill welcome even a famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want to be a substitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sonoko asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the housekeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where the headmaster is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the building in the middle of the pond, the tea room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's simple and artistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a wabi-sabi world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's definitely the tea room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's built in the middle of the pond that changes colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called "Five Colors."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a tea room that was built for a break from everyday business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's called "Five Colors."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a nice tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is the headmaster's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.80,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ryoichi Aonogi (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.80,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Headmaster's son
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:38.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've already heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell the famous detective about the demon as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's like the superstition of this pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do not talk about that. I only came here to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if you'll excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Mimura-san
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of Ryoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's talk about this over there while we drink hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say it was during the end of the Edo period.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fresh, clean, cold water sprang out from the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was even bigger than it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A beautiful girl appeared by the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As she played her flute, the color of the pond changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She entertained the people who came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a rich merchant became interested in the girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and built a mansion near the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She accepted his proposal of marriage with two conditions:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the pond belonged to her, and no one was ever to go in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet, the merchant broke his promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made a bedroom in the middle of the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In addition,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he became angry at his wife who pressed\Nhim to clear the room away immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And drowned her in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, one night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the boa that appeared from the lake attacked the merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The demon who lived in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Terribly wounded and with great difficulty,\Nthe merchant went in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the bedroom, there were talismans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, the demon waited for him to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got tired and hung himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say the reason why the colors change,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is because the demon takes the girl's\Nappearance and plays the flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe that there's such a horrible\Nlegend in such a beautiful pond...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come to the tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoichi-san isn't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he's the headmaster's only son,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's not interested in tea ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I haven't greeted the headmaster yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master rarely comes out these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He won't ever cross this bridge alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've brought the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was eaten by the demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spying on people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think this sacred place is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our guest, Mouri-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The substitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a waterwheel over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that waterwheel a decoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It gives water to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's electrically-powered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the timer, it should turn at the decided time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At one time, it was famous for tea water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after this tea room was made, the amount of water just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shh! Mimura-san, Master will hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about my rude behavior earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stay all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talismans...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}are{\i0} scared of the demon in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see what I told Hanasaki-san to give to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An owner of Kyushu's ceramics factory gave it to\Nme, which was passed down many generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:03.83,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ryouzou Aono (65)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:03.83,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Tea Ceremony Headmaster
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's impressive that you got such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:03.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But you are an antique dealer after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's use the teacup at tonight's tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tea ceremony will be even better with the teacup.\NI deserve it, after all, this is my last tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "last"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri-san, I got the best, old sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki, prepare the sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last tea...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My leg's asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, it's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get ready for the tea ceremony tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one is to come near the tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a small errand to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master is going to host the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yakura-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bath is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you do that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa! The pond's color changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun's reflection is gone and you can\Nsee inside the pond. It looks green.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll turn red when the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki-san, why are these fishing rods...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master told me to burn them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mustn't, Ryoichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoichi, guests are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until tonight's tea ceremony is over, you should wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to put these away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fishing is Ryoichi's only hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master can do such harsh things...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But yelling all of the sudden and burning the\Nfishing rods, instead of hard to please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last year, when the tea room was completed, his wife died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His wife believed in the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she was against building the tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a similar story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Between us pupils, there have been rumors where\Nsome have seen the demon's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the headmaster is afraid of the\Ndemon, which makes him hard to please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says it's a stupid superstition and laughs it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go get the hot water ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then. I'm going to go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there are really demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you catch that big fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering where you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat some snacks in the guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeeees!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in Ryoichi-san's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a giant fish print hung in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoichi is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes he invites me to go night fishing with\Nhim, but I can never be as good as him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security sensor. Looks like someone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's looking around restlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's red!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so bright, I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's four o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around this time, the sun makes a diffused reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki-san, do you have a cold drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mimura-san, where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her kimono is a mess and she's sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have really been in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the arrogant attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Master's tea ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To sneak out in the middle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now now, both of you, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't we talking about the last tea ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were looking forward to his retirement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that supposed to mean, Mimura-san!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't assume things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes yes, I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sucks. Even the pond looks heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's... the headmaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use, it's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any other entrances?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One to the water room in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water room is locked too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no other choice but to break in then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the legend! Master was killed by the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means Mouri-san is here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mouri-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not happy at all to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I collected all of the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entrance was locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the screen was slightly open, but there were bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on the east side, there was a water room, but it was also locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death was 3:30 to 4:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was bleeding, but he died from the\Npressure on his neck and it being choked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's suicide, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The headmaster cut his wrists on the\Nveranda to commit suicide at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was unsuccessful so he hung himself in the tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:19:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would explain the trail of blood\Nfrom here to inside the tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was unsuccessful at the veranda and committed suicide in the\Ntea room, then I don't think he would be able to lock the doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The waterwheel is turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So narrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pinhole on the inside of the entrance door...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cut end of the rope is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it was cut halfway by a sharp object,\Nand then the other half was ripped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scroll is spread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was probably getting ready for tonight's tea ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While he was preparing, he suddenly chose death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't finished writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This stuff is wood pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even on the tatami mat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the beam that the rope was hung from!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? There's no mark, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't see very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-yo, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since when did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bother us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have a piggy-back ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go away, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a mark where the rope wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's new!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-ahh!! U-Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killed by the legendary demon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, do you really think that we police are going to believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-We're positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood marks on the veranda and the\Nway he died is all similar to the legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if there was no demon, he died just like in the legend,\Nwhich would mean that he was killed by the demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have made this tea room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right after it was made, the wife died because\Nof a heart attack, and now, the headmaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was mentally stressed out, so he definitely committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:22:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of these people used a clever trick to kill the\Nheadmaster and made it look like a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real demon who blames it on a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:24.48,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Natsu no Maboroshi
